---
layout: base
title: "Thank You"
description: Your message has been received.
permalink: /thank-you/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-16); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">
  <div class="container--prose" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">

    <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Message Received</h1>

    <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose); max-width: 50ch; margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);">
      Thank you for writing. We read every message and will respond if a reply is needed.
    </p>

    <p style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ink-faint); max-width: 50ch; margin: 0 auto var(--space-10);">
      If you included an email address and your message requires a response, expect to hear from us within a few business days.
    </p>

    <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule); padding-top: var(--space-8); max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-10);">
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">While you're here</p>
      {% set subscribeVariant = "inline" %}
      {% include "partials/subscribe.njk" %}
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: var(--text-sm);">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--color-link); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Home</a>
      <span style="color: var(--color-rule);">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/start-here/" style="color: var(--color-link); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Start Here</a>
      <span style="color: var(--color-rule);">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/library/" style="color: var(--color-link); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Library</a>
      <span style="color: var(--color-rule);">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/quotes/" style="color: var(--color-link); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Quotes</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
